        "content": "### Classify with AI\n\nLLM classification into: P1, P2, P3 (+fallback). Output port order matches this list.\n\nPorts: ①→ Store as P1 · ②→ Store as P2 · ③→ Store as P3 · ④→ Alert Outlook — Other",
